'''Microsoft Entourage'''是[[微軟|微軟]]為[[Mac_OS|Mac OS]] 8.5或以上版本開發的[[郵箱客戶端|郵箱客戶端]]及[[個人信息管理系統|個人信息管理系統]]。[[微軟|微軟]]最先於2000年10月以[[Microsoft_Office|Microsoft Office 2001]]的一部分發佈'''Entourage'''；而上一個[[Mac_OS|Mac OS]]版本的[[Microsoft_Office|Microsoft Office]]，Office 98，則包括了[[Outlook_Express|Outlook Express 5]]。目前最新的版本是Entourage: Mac 2008，是於2008年1月15日發佈的[[Microsoft_Office_2008_for_Mac|Microsoft Office 2008 for Mac]]的一部份。

[[微软|微软]]于2010年10月26日发售[[Microsoft_Office_2011_for_Mac|Microsoft Office 2011 for Mac]]，并用[[Microsoft_Outlook|Microsoft Outlook]]取代了'''Entourage'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/123107.htm |title=微软10月26日发售Office for Mac 2011 |accessdate=2015-07-12 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304125849/http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/123107.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 概略 ==
Entourage是一個[[郵箱客戶端|郵箱客戶端]]，同時亦可以管理[[日曆|日曆]]，[[地址簿|地址簿]]，[[行事曆|行事曆]]及專案管理員。而[[微軟|微軟]]從Entourage 2004開始，提供專案中心（Project Center）功能，用戶可以透過此功能建立及整體不同的專案。Entourage中的資訊可以是來自Entourage本身或是從外部獲取。Entourage支援以[[POP|POP]]或[[IMAP|IMAP]]方式<ref>{{cite web  |publisher=Microsoft MVPs: The Entourage Help Page  |url=http://www.entourage.mvps.org/accounts/index.html  |title=Accounts  |date=2008-08-21  |accessdate=2008-08-26  |archive-date=2005-12-18  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051218234249/http://www.entourage.mvps.org/accounts/index.html  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>及以[[WebDAV|WebDAV]]（使用[[Microsoft_Exchange|Microsoft Exchange]]伺服器）方式接收郵件<ref>{{cite web  |publisher=Microsoft: The Entourage Help Page  |url=http://www.entourage.mvps.org/exchange/faqs.html#exup10  |title=FAQs for Exchange 2004  |date=2008-08-17  |accessdate=2008-08-26  |archive-date=2005-12-19  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051219010804/http://www.entourage.mvps.org/exchange/faqs.html#exup10  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>。

Entourage 2008提供了“My Day”工具，可以協助用戶組織日程，提高搜尋速度，“to do”標幟，改良了的垃圾郵件過濾，[[釣魚式攻擊|網絡釣魚]]保護，於Favourites的快速瀏覽及可以自訂的工具列。

== 功能 ==
Entourage支援一些Mac OS的技術，例如[[Spotlight|Spotlight]]搜尋引擎及[[AppleScript|AppleScript]]。但因其龐大的資料庫，令Time Machine不能有效地備份。Entourage亦有一個獨立的[[通訊錄|通訊錄]]，但可以使用[[iSync|iSync]]同步處理連絡人及行事曆。<ref>{{cite magazine  |last=Negrino  |first=Tom  |url=http://www.macworld.com/article/131563/2008/01/entourage2008.html  |journal=[[Macworld|Macworld]]  |title=Microsoft Entourage 2008 - Superior depth of features bests Apple competitor  |date=2008-01-21  |accessdate=2008-08-26  |archive-date=2012-02-23  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223221231/http://www.macworld.com/article/131563/2008/01/entourage2008.html  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>。
=== 與Outlook的比較 ===
與其他Mac版本[[Microsoft_Office|Office]]不同的是，Entourage不使用Windows版本產品的名稱。而微軟則認為Entourage是為了「滿足完全不同的觀眾的需求」<ref>{{cite web |publisher = Microsoft: The Entourage Help Page |url = http://www.entourage.mvps.org/articles/entourage.html |title = Entourage is not Outlook |first = Michel |last = Bintener |date = 2008-08-17 |accessdate = 2008-08-26 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081107114248/http://www.entourage.mvps.org/articles/entourage.html |archivedate = 2008-11-07 }}</ref>。Entourage源自Mac版本的[[Outlook_Express|Outlook Express]] 5及[[Claris_Emailer|Claris Emailer]]<ref>{{cite web  |last=Ross  |first=Dianne  |publisher=Microsoft: The Entourage help Page  |url=http://blog.entourage.mvps.org/2007/05/in_the_beginning.html  |title=In the Beginning  |date=2007-05-20  |accessdate=2008-08-26  |archive-date=2008-06-24  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080624084550/http://blog.entourage.mvps.org/2007/05/in_the_beginning.html  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>，而Entourage是“no ported code, and no Office code”，即是沒有Outlook及Office的代碼<ref>{{cite web  |last=Shahine  |first=Omar  |publisher=MSDN Blogs  |url=http://blogs.msdn.com/omars/archive/2004/04/05/107468.aspx  |title=Entourage: A journey to becoming an Office application  |date=2004-04-04  |accessdate=2008-08-26  |archive-date=2004-06-17  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040617142600/http://blogs.msdn.com/omars/archive/2004/04/05/107468.aspx  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>。不過，微軟將Entourage定位成為Macintosh的Exchange用戶而設的「相似」產品<ref>{{cite web   |publisher=Microsoft   |url=http://www.microsoft.com/mac/support.aspx?pid=exchange   |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050207151545/http://www.microsoft.com/mac/support.aspx?pid=exchange   |archivedate=2005-02-07   |title=Working with Exchange Server   |date=2004-08-04   |accessdate=2008-08-26   |deadurl=yes   }}</ref>。

=== Microsoft Exchange的客戶端 ===
Entourage自2003年8月4日發佈Entourage X的更新之後，開始支援Microsoft Exchange伺服器。這個早期的版本需要使用[[IMAP|IMAP]]以支援郵件收發及WebDAV以支援[[通訊錄|通訊錄]]及行事曆的功能。（其後的版本已不需要IMAP而全面使用WebDAV。）用戶亦投訴Windows版本Outlook及Entourage 2001功能不足。<ref>{{cite web  |publisher  = MacWindows.com  |url  = http://www.macwindows.com/entourage#8  |title  = Using Entourage with Exchange Server Special Report  |date  = 2003-08-06  |accessdate  = 2008-08-26  |deadurl  = yes  |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20081011061831/http://www.macwindows.com/entourage#8  |archivedate  = 2008-10-11  }}</ref>其後的版本亦有加入部份缺少的功能。但是Entourage 2008仍不是與Outlook一樣的Exchange客戶端<ref>{{cite magazine  |last=Welch  |first=John C.  |url=http://www.macworld.com/article/131730/2008/01/msftexchange.html  |journal=[[Macworld|Macworld]]  |title=How Entourage 2008 fares with Exchange - Update improves Mac-Exchange relationship, though some features still undone  |date=2008-01-21  |accessdate=2008-08-26  |archive-date=2012-02-20  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120220121421/http://www.macworld.com/article/131730/2008/01/msftexchange.html  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>。例如Entourage 2008仍不能將待辦事項及筆記與Exchange伺服器同步化。很多Exchange用戶都於口頭上<ref>{{cite web  |last=Smith  |first=William M.  |url=http://blog.entourage.mvps.org/2008/01/prioritize_your_exchange_needs.html  |title=Prioritize your Exchange Needs!  |date=2008-01-17  |accessdate=2008-08-26  |archive-date=2010-09-23  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100923120800/http://blog.entourage.mvps.org/2008/01/prioritize_your_exchange_needs.html  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>指責微軟於此的過失<ref>{{cite magazine |last = Flynn  |first = David  |url         = http://apcmag.com/7842/office_2008_for_mac_fails_to_deliver_full_exchange_support  |journal     = [[APC_(magazine)|APC Magazine]]
 |title  = Office 2008 for Mac fails to deliver full Exchange support  |date        = 2008-01-17  |accessdate  = 2008-08-26  |deadurl     = yes  |archiveurl  = http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20110915181828/http://apcmag.com/7842/office_2008_for_mac_fails_to_deliver_full_exchange_support  |archivedate = 2011-09-15 }}</ref>。微軟則解釋指，於Entoruage 2008中，程式的「可靠程度」比Exchange支援更重要。<ref>{{cite news  |last=Keizer  |first=Gregg  |url=http://www.computerworlduk.com/technology/applications/desktop/news-analysis/index.cfm?articleid=1094  |publisher=[[Computerworld|Computerworld UK]]  |title=In Mac Office 2008, reliability trumps Exchange support  |date=2008-01-14  |accessdate=2008-08-26  |archive-date=2019-10-18  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191018122445/https://www.computerworld.com/uk/  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>.

